# Childcare Cost Impact

This project explores how childcare costs affect U.S. families by income level, using state-level datasets. The analysis highlights affordability challenges and burden disparities.

## ğŸ“Š Objective

To evaluate the financial burden of childcare across income groups and geographic locations.

## ğŸ“ Dataset

- U.S. Department of Labor National Database of Childcare Prices (2022)
- Median household income by state
- Family composition data

